nodes.text: The Empire Strikes Back Monthly 150 is the one hundred fiftieth issue of the Marvel Star Wars UK series of comic books.

As the cover tease shows, this issue was intended to include part one of The Pandora Effect, but a note on the first page says deadline woes made it impossible to include in this issue. Instead, it reprints Star Wars 16. The Pandora Effect was printed entirely in The Empire Strikes Back Monthly 151.
